description:
Good evening ,ladies and gentleman, here comes our Warframe :Fashion time again, I’m your host here, I give you…   Octavia! The precure skin!   
feel free to use this music as BG music when you look at this artwork: 
 
[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eTI8hgWJh-I](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eTI8hgWJh-I) 
 
 Give your Octavia the most dazzling and beautiful looking,  MLP’s Octavia? Warframe’s Octavia? Precure style? (about the DJ I drew many days ago. [Here](https://www.derpibooru.org/1560148))    
 
Why not, Three!?    
 
Because this new design with the most beautiful looking warframe ,provide the power of fashion and adorableness but also carry devastating power that can bring every Grineers and Cropus and Infested dancing with her samba of death.    
 
This design idea was orginial from the meme video about Warframe Octavia (no MLP Octavia) in Youtube created by Mr.WarframeGuy.  
the video is here:  
[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LqdepDu3lqE](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LqdepDu3lqE) 
 
you can imaging Octaiva(MLP octaiva with Warframe Octavia) in this video dancing just adorable as hell  
 And it gives me the idea of this. And I also want to present it as the second precure ballet series artwork after DJ pon3 one, instead of it’s not Ballet this time,  it’s samba, but you know. With exquisite looking and the spirit of the lovely Octavia, the charm are only getting up and up.   Hope you like my Octavia’s skin desgin, Warframe Octavia, MLP’s Octavia and precure Octavia, trinity. Combine~give Canterlot Royal ballet Academy series something different.  
 
 Maybe I will make this skin present to DE , and don’t tring to stop me. (RD face)    
 
Sean.M
